[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1077},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fai\u002F20260320\u002F2827818448\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fai\u002F20260320\u002F2827818448\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fai\u002F20260320\u002F2827818448\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fai\u002F20260320\u002F2827818448\u002F":1054,"related:\u002Fai\u002F20260320\u002F2827818448\u002F":1062},"\u002Fen\u002Fai\u002F2026\u002F03\u002F20\u002Fclaude-code-channels-instead-of-openclaw\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1032,"date":1033,"description":1034,"extension":1035,"lang":1036,"meta":1037,"navigation":1038,"path":1039,"readingMinutes":1040,"seo":1041,"standalone":1042,"stem":1043,"tags":1044,"tldr":1050,"updated":1051,"url":1052,"__hash__":1053},"content\u002Fai\u002F不想用龍蝦-OpenClaw-來試試看-Claude-Code-channels-吧！.md","不想用龍蝦（OpenClaw）？來試試看 Claude Code channels 吧！","2827818448",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1017},"minimark",[11,18,28,32,35,38,41,45,48,51,54,57,60,64,67,101,104,109,112,115,148,151,162,165,178,181,185,192,195,211,218,224,231,247,250,255,260,268,276,281,288,299,303,306,323,326,329,334,341,346,352,361,366,369,374,377,391,397,400,423,434,439,453,456,459,465,475,478,501,507,510,525,528,534,538,541,548,557,563,566,572,575,580,585,588,594,597,603,609,629,635,638,644,649,652,666,672,675,693,704,709,723,726,732,737,740,760,776,779,792,795,801,817,821,824,827,830,845,858,861,865,868,961,964,981,984,987,1013],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":6,"src":17},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002FGemini_Generated_Image_307jf3307jf3307j_1280x714.png",[19,20,21],"blockquote",{},[12,22,23,27],{},[24,25,26],"strong",{},"Note","\nClaude Code channels 是 Anthropic 推出的官方解法，可以把外部事件（Telegram、Discord）推送進 Claude Code Session。跟第三方的龍蝦（OpenClaw）相比，channels 偏向「事件驅動」（推送 CI 結果、警報），龍蝦則是用聊天平台直接操控電腦。",[29,30,31],"h2",{"id":31},"前言",[12,33,34],{},"如果你有在關注 AI Agent 相關的工具，應該多少聽過龍蝦（OpenClaw）這個工具吧？簡單來講，龍蝦可以讓你透過聊天平台來遠端操控電腦上的 AI Agent，但其實 Claude Code 最近也推出了類似的功能，叫做「Channels」。",[12,36,37],{},"Channels 的概念跟龍蝦非常類似，都是讓你可以透過外部平台（像是 Telegram、Discord）來對正在運行的 Claude Code Session 發送訊息，讓 Claude 可以在背景幫你處理任務。不同的是，Channels 是 Anthropic 官方推出的功能，所以在穩定性和安全性上會更有保障，也不用擔心被判定為違規操作。",[12,39,40],{},"那這篇文章就來帶大家了解 Channels 是什麼、怎麼設定、以及實際上要怎麼使用吧。",[29,42,44],{"id":43},"claude-code-channels-是什麼","Claude Code Channels 是什麼？",[12,46,47],{},"簡單來講，Channel 其實就是一個 MCP Server，它可以把外部的事件（訊息、通知、Webhook 等）推送到你正在運行的 Claude Code Session 中，讓 Claude 能夠在你不在終端機前的時候，也能夠對這些事件做出反應。",[12,49,50],{},"而且 Channels 是雙向的——Claude 不只可以接收訊息，還可以透過同一個 Channel 回覆訊息。舉例來說，你在 Telegram 上傳一段訊息給 Bot，Claude 會在終端機中處理這個請求，然後把結果回傳到 Telegram 上，你就可以直接在手機上看到結果了。",[12,52,53],{},"這邊要注意的是，當 Claude 透過 Channel 回覆的時候，你在終端機上只會看到 inbound 的訊息和工具呼叫的確認（像是「sent」），實際的回覆內容會出現在另一個平台上（例如 Telegram 或 Discord）。",[12,55,56],{},"不過事件只有在 Session 開啟的時候才會到達，所以如果你想要 24 小時不間斷的接收訊息的話，你就需要讓 Claude Code 在背景程序或持久化的終端機中持續運行唷。",[12,58,59],{},"另外補充一下，Channels 目前還是 Research Preview 階段，需要 Claude Code v2.1.80 或以上版本，而且只支援 claude.ai 登入，不支援 Console 或 API Key 認證。如果你是 Team 或 Enterprise 方案的話，管理員需要先啟用才能使用。",[29,61,63],{"id":62},"開始之前要準備什麼","開始之前要準備什麼？",[12,65,66],{},"在開始設定之前，你需要先確認以下幾件事：",[68,69,70,79,86],"ul",{},[71,72,73,74,78],"li",{},"Claude Code v2.1.80 或以上版本（可以用 ",[75,76,77],"code",{},"claude --version"," 來確認）",[71,80,81,82,85],{},"claude.ai 帳號（需要透過 ",[75,83,84],{},"\u002Flogin"," 登入，不支援 API Key）",[71,87,88,89,96,97,100],{},"安裝 ",[90,91,95],"a",{"href":92,"rel":93},"https:\u002F\u002Fbun.sh",[94],"nofollow","Bun","（Channel Plugin 是用 Bun 來運行的，可以用 ",[75,98,99],{},"bun --version"," 來確認有沒有安裝）",[12,102,103],{},"這些東西如果沒有準備好的話，後面的步驟是沒辦法順利進行的唷。",[105,106,108],"h3",{"id":107},"安裝-bun","安裝 Bun",[12,110,111],{},"Channel Plugin 都是用 Bun 來跑的，所以這邊要先安裝一下。如果你已經有裝過的話可以跳過這一段。",[12,113,114],{},"macOS \u002F Linux \u002F WSL：",[116,117,122],"pre",{"className":118,"code":119,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","curl -fsSL https:\u002F\u002Fbun.sh\u002Finstall | bash\n","bash","",[75,123,124],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,126,129,133,137,141,145],"span",{"class":127,"line":128},"line",1,[125,130,132],{"class":131},"s_sBn","curl",[125,134,136],{"class":135},"sCcAr"," -fsSL",[125,138,140],{"class":139},"sTRMh"," https:\u002F\u002Fbun.sh\u002Finstall",[125,142,144],{"class":143},"sWyjQ"," |",[125,146,147],{"class":131}," bash\n",[12,149,150],{},"Windows PowerShell：",[116,152,156],{"className":153,"code":154,"language":155,"meta":121,"style":121},"language-powershell shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","powershell -c \"irm bun.sh\u002Finstall.ps1 | iex\"\n","powershell",[75,157,158],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,159,160],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,161,154],{},[12,163,164],{},"安裝完之後可以用以下指令來確認有沒有安裝成功：",[116,166,168],{"className":118,"code":167,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"bun --version\n",[75,169,170],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,171,172,175],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,173,174],{"class":131},"bun",[125,176,177],{"class":135}," --version\n",[12,179,180],{},"如果有正確跑出版本號的話就代表安裝成功囉～",[29,182,184],{"id":183},"先用-fakechat-來體驗看看","先用 fakechat 來體驗看看",[12,186,187,188,191],{},"在正式設定 Telegram 或 Discord 之前，我們可以先用官方提供的 ",[24,189,190],{},"fakechat"," 來體驗一下 Channels 的運作方式。fakechat 是一個在 localhost 上運行的聊天 UI，不需要任何外部服務或認證，非常適合拿來測試。",[12,193,194],{},"首先啟動一個 Claude Code Session，然後輸入以下指令來安裝 fakechat Plugin：",[116,196,198],{"className":118,"code":197,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"\u002Fplugin install fakechat@claude-plugins-official\n",[75,199,200],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,201,202,205,208],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,203,204],{"class":131},"\u002Fplugin",[125,206,207],{"class":139}," install",[125,209,210],{"class":139}," fakechat@claude-plugins-official\n",[19,212,213],{},[12,214,215,217],{},[24,216,26],{},"\n輸入之後，請記得重啟 Claude Code，讓 Plugin 被正確載入，否則後續的設定指令可能會找不到唷。",[12,219,220],{},[15,221],{"alt":222,"src":223},"安裝畫面","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320144433.png",[12,225,226,227,230],{},"安裝完成之後，先退出 Claude Code，然後用 ",[75,228,229],{},"--channels"," 參數重新啟動：",[116,232,234],{"className":118,"code":233,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"claude --channels plugin:fakechat@claude-plugins-official\n",[75,235,236],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,237,238,241,244],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,239,240],{"class":131},"claude",[125,242,243],{"class":135}," --channels",[125,245,246],{"class":139}," plugin:fakechat@claude-plugins-official\n",[12,248,249],{},"這樣 fakechat 的伺服器就會自動啟動了。",[12,251,252],{},[15,253],{"alt":190,"src":254},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320145628.png",[12,256,257],{},[15,258],{"alt":190,"src":259},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320145653.png",[12,261,262,263,267],{},"接著打開瀏覽器，前往 ",[90,264,265],{"href":265,"rel":266},"http:\u002F\u002Flocalhost:8787",[94],"，你會看到一個簡單的聊天介面，試著輸入一段訊息，例如：",[116,269,274],{"className":270,"code":272,"language":273,"meta":121},[271],"language-text","哈囉你好\n","text",[75,275,272],{"__ignoreMap":121},[12,277,278],{},[15,279],{"alt":190,"src":280},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320145339.png",[12,282,283,284,287],{},"這時候訊息就會被推送到你的 Claude Code Session 中，Claude 會讀取訊息並處理，然後透過 fakechat 的 ",[75,285,286],{},"reply"," 工具把結果回傳到聊天介面上，你就可以直接在瀏覽器上看到結果囉～",[19,289,290],{},[12,291,292,294,295,298],{},[24,293,26],{},"\n如果 Claude 在執行過程中遇到權限提示，Session 會暫停直到你在終端機上手動核准。如果你想要完全無人值守的話，可以用 ",[75,296,297],{},"--dangerously-skip-permissions"," 來跳過權限提示，但請只在你信任的環境中使用唷。",[29,300,302],{"id":301},"設定-telegram-channel","設定 Telegram Channel",[12,304,305],{},"體驗完 fakechat 之後，接下來我們就來設定真正的 Telegram Channel 吧！",[12,307,308,309,314,315,318,319,322],{},"首先打開 Telegram，搜尋 ",[90,310,313],{"href":311,"rel":312},"https:\u002F\u002Ft.me\u002FBotFather",[94],"BotFather"," 並發送 ",[75,316,317],{},"\u002Fnewbot","，接著依照指示給你的 Bot 設定一個顯示名稱和一個以 ",[75,320,321],{},"bot"," 結尾的使用者名稱。設定完成後，BotFather 會回傳一組 Token，把它複製起來。",[12,324,325],{},"但為了確保大家順利，這邊還是寫了一下步驟：",[12,327,328],{},"搜尋 @BotFather 並建立新 Bot，剛進去會看到這樣的畫面：",[12,330,331],{},[15,332],{"alt":313,"src":333},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002FIMG_1609.jpg",[19,335,336],{},[12,337,338,340],{},[24,339,26],{},"\n請注意必須要有認證的藍勾勾的才是真的 BotFather 不是我底下打紅叉叉的假 BotFather 喔～",[12,342,343],{},[15,344],{"alt":313,"src":345},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002FIMG_1610.jpg",[12,347,348,349,351],{},"接著輸入 ",[75,350,317],{}," 來建立一個新的 Bot，BotFather 會先問你「Alright, a new bot. How are we going to call it? Please choose a name for your bot.」，意思是「你要替你的 Bot 取什麼名字呢？」這個名字可以隨便取，之後也可以改，所以不用太在意。",[12,353,354,355,357,358,360],{},"接著會問你「Good. Now let's choose a username for your bot. It must end in ",[75,356,321],{},".」，意思是「好，現在幫你的 Bot 選一個使用者名稱吧！必須要以 ",[75,359,321],{}," 結尾喔！」這個使用者名稱是 Telegram 上的唯一識別碼，不能跟其他 Bot 重複，所以可能需要試幾次才能找到一個可用的。",[12,362,363],{},[15,364],{"alt":313,"src":365},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002FIMG_1611.jpg",[12,367,368],{},"最後你就可以拿到 HTTP API Token 啦！它會是一串由英文字母、數字和冒號組成的長字串，請把它記下來（也請不要分享或者外流給他人）。",[12,370,371],{},[15,372],{"alt":313,"src":373},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002FIMG_1612.jpg",[12,375,376],{},"接著回到 Claude Code，輸入以下指令來安裝 Telegram Plugin：",[116,378,380],{"className":118,"code":379,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"\u002Fplugin install telegram@claude-plugins-official\n",[75,381,382],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,383,384,386,388],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,385,204],{"class":131},[125,387,207],{"class":139},[125,389,390],{"class":139}," telegram@claude-plugins-official\n",[19,392,393],{},[12,394,395,217],{},[24,396,26],{},[12,398,399],{},"安裝完之後，用剛剛從 BotFather 取得的 Token 來設定：",[116,401,403],{"className":118,"code":402,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"\u002Ftelegram:configure \u003Ctoken>\n",[75,404,405],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,406,407,410,413,416,420],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,408,409],{"class":131},"\u002Ftelegram:configure",[125,411,412],{"class":143}," \u003C",[125,414,415],{"class":139},"toke",[125,417,419],{"class":418},"sMAXC","n",[125,421,422],{"class":143},">\n",[12,424,425,426,429,430,433],{},"這會把 Token 儲存在專案的 ",[75,427,428],{},".claude\u002Fchannels\u002Ftelegram\u002F.env"," 中。當然你也可以在啟動 Claude Code 之前，先在 Shell 環境中設定 ",[75,431,432],{},"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN"," 環境變數，這樣就不用每次都跑 configure 了。",[12,435,436,437,230],{},"設定完之後，退出 Claude Code，然後帶上 ",[75,438,229],{},[116,440,442],{"className":118,"code":441,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"claude --channels plugin:telegram@claude-plugins-official\n",[75,443,444],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,445,446,448,450],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,447,240],{"class":131},[125,449,243],{"class":135},[125,451,452],{"class":139}," plugin:telegram@claude-plugins-official\n",[12,454,455],{},"這會啟動 Telegram Plugin，開始輪詢你的 Bot 的訊息。",[12,457,458],{},"接著打開 Telegram，對你的 Bot 發送任何一段訊息，Bot 就會回覆你一組配對碼。",[12,460,461],{},[15,462],{"alt":463,"src":464},"Telegram Bot","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002FIMG_1613.jpg",[19,466,467],{},[12,468,469,471,472,474],{},[24,470,26],{},"\n如果你的 Bot 沒有回應，請確認 Claude Code 是不是有帶 ",[75,473,229],{}," 參數在運行中，因為 Bot 只有在 Channel 啟動的狀態下才能回覆唷。",[12,476,477],{},"拿到配對碼之後，回到 Claude Code 輸入：",[116,479,481],{"className":118,"code":480,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"\u002Ftelegram:access pair \u003Ccode>\n",[75,482,483],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,484,485,488,491,493,496,499],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,486,487],{"class":131},"\u002Ftelegram:access",[125,489,490],{"class":139}," pair",[125,492,412],{"class":143},[125,494,495],{"class":139},"cod",[125,497,498],{"class":418},"e",[125,500,422],{"class":143},[12,502,503],{},[15,504],{"alt":505,"src":506},"配對碼","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320151558.png",[12,508,509],{},"然後記得鎖定存取權限，確保只有你的帳號可以發送訊息：",[116,511,513],{"className":118,"code":512,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"\u002Ftelegram:access policy allowlist\n",[75,514,515],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,516,517,519,522],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,518,487],{"class":131},[125,520,521],{"class":139}," policy",[125,523,524],{"class":139}," allowlist\n",[12,526,527],{},"這樣就設定完成囉！你現在可以直接透過 Telegram 對 Claude Code 下指令了～",[12,529,530],{},[15,531],{"alt":532,"src":533},"下指令","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202026-03-20%2015.19.38.png",[29,535,537],{"id":536},"設定-discord-channel","設定 Discord Channel",[12,539,540],{},"如果你比較常用 Discord 的話，也可以選擇設定 Discord Channel，步驟跟 Telegram 類似，但多了一些 Discord 特有的設定。",[19,542,543],{},[12,544,545,547],{},[24,546,26],{},"\n小提醒一下，建議你先建立一個自己的 Discord 伺服器會比較好後續的操作。",[12,549,550,551,556],{},"首先前往 ",[90,552,555],{"href":553,"rel":554},"https:\u002F\u002Fdiscord.com\u002Fdevelopers\u002Fapplications",[94],"Discord Developer Portal","，點選「New Application」並設定名稱",[12,558,559],{},[15,560],{"alt":561,"src":562},"Discord Bot","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152138.png",[12,564,565],{},"接著側邊欄找到「Bot」",[12,567,568],{},[15,569],{"alt":570,"src":571},"Bot","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152312.png",[12,573,574],{},"然後點選「Reset Token」並複製 Token",[12,576,577],{},[15,578],{"alt":561,"src":579},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152222.png",[12,581,582],{},[15,583],{"alt":561,"src":584},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152247.png",[12,586,587],{},"接著在 Bot 的設定頁面中，往下滑到「Privileged Gateway Intents」，把「Message Content Intent」啟用，這個很重要，如果沒有啟用的話 Bot 是讀不到訊息內容的。",[12,589,590],{},[15,591],{"alt":592,"src":593},"Message Content Intent","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152531.png",[12,595,596],{},"接著側邊欄找到「OAuth2」",[12,598,599],{},[15,600],{"alt":601,"src":602},"OAuth2","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152634.png",[12,604,605,606,608],{},"然後前往「URL Generator」，勾選 ",[75,607,321],{}," 範圍，然後啟用以下權限：",[68,610,611,614,617,620,623,626],{},[71,612,613],{},"檢視頻道（View Channels）",[71,615,616],{},"發送訊息（Send Messages）",[71,618,619],{},"讀取訊息歷史（Read Message History）",[71,621,622],{},"在討論串中發送訊息（Send Messages in Threads）",[71,624,625],{},"附加檔案（Attach Files）",[71,627,628],{},"加入反應（Add Reactions）",[12,630,631],{},[15,632],{"alt":633,"src":634},"權限","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320152838.png",[12,636,637],{},"打開產生的網址，把 Bot 加入你的伺服器。",[12,639,640],{},[15,641],{"alt":642,"src":643},"加入伺服器","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320153104.png",[12,645,646],{},[15,647],{"alt":642,"src":648},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320153150.png",[12,650,651],{},"接著回到 Claude Code，安裝 Discord Plugin：",[116,653,655],{"className":118,"code":654,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"\u002Fplugin install discord@claude-plugins-official\n",[75,656,657],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,658,659,661,663],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,660,204],{"class":131},[125,662,207],{"class":139},[125,664,665],{"class":139}," discord@claude-plugins-official\n",[19,667,668],{},[12,669,670,217],{},[24,671,26],{},[12,673,674],{},"安裝完之後，設定剛剛複製的 Token：",[116,676,678],{"className":118,"code":677,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"\u002Fdiscord:configure \u003Ctoken>\n",[75,679,680],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,681,682,685,687,689,691],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,683,684],{"class":131},"\u002Fdiscord:configure",[125,686,412],{"class":143},[125,688,415],{"class":139},[125,690,419],{"class":418},[125,692,422],{"class":143},[12,694,695,696,699,700,703],{},"跟 Telegram 一樣，Token 會被儲存在 ",[75,697,698],{},".claude\u002Fchannels\u002Fdiscord\u002F.env"," 中，你也可以用 ",[75,701,702],{},"DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN"," 環境變數來設定。",[12,705,706,707,230],{},"設定完退出 Claude Code，帶上 ",[75,708,229],{},[116,710,712],{"className":118,"code":711,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"claude --channels plugin:discord@claude-plugins-official\n",[75,713,714],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,715,716,718,720],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,717,240],{"class":131},[125,719,243],{"class":135},[125,721,722],{"class":139}," plugin:discord@claude-plugins-official\n",[12,724,725],{},"接著從你邀請 Bot 的 Discord 伺服器中，對 Bot 發送任何一段訊息，Bot 就會回覆你一組配對碼",[12,727,728],{},[15,729],{"alt":730,"src":731},"對話","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320153512.png",[12,733,734],{},[15,735],{"alt":730,"src":736},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fclaude-code-channels\u002F20260320153652.png",[12,738,739],{},"回到 Claude Code 完成配對：",[116,741,743],{"className":118,"code":742,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"\u002Fdiscord:access pair \u003Ccode>\n",[75,744,745],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,746,747,750,752,754,756,758],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,748,749],{"class":131},"\u002Fdiscord:access",[125,751,490],{"class":139},[125,753,412],{"class":143},[125,755,495],{"class":139},[125,757,498],{"class":418},[125,759,422],{"class":143},[19,761,762],{},[12,763,764,766,767,770,771],{},[24,765,26],{},"\n這邊我有遇到一個狀況，就是配對碼一直過期，所以我改用 ",[75,768,769],{},"\u002Fdiscord:access allow \u003CsenderId>"," 直接把自己 Discord 的發送者 ID 加入白名單。如果你不知道該如何取得 Discord ID，你可以參考這篇文章：",[90,772,775],{"href":773,"rel":774},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fother\u002F20211013\u002F4225269670\u002F",[94],"一篇教你輕鬆取得自己的 Discord ID",[12,777,778],{},"然後一樣鎖定存取權限：",[116,780,782],{"className":118,"code":781,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"\u002Fdiscord:access policy allowlist\n",[75,783,784],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,785,786,788,790],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,787,749],{"class":131},[125,789,521],{"class":139},[125,791,524],{"class":139},[12,793,794],{},"這樣就完成啦～",[12,796,797,798,800],{},"當然，如果你想同時啟用多個 Channel 的話，可以在 ",[75,799,229],{}," 後面用空格分隔多個 Plugin，像是這樣：",[116,802,804],{"className":118,"code":803,"language":120,"meta":121,"style":121},"claude --channels plugin:telegram@claude-plugins-official plugin:discord@claude-plugins-official\n",[75,805,806],{"__ignoreMap":121},[125,807,808,810,812,815],{"class":127,"line":128},[125,809,240],{"class":131},[125,811,243],{"class":135},[125,813,814],{"class":139}," plugin:telegram@claude-plugins-official",[125,816,722],{"class":139},[29,818,820],{"id":819},"channels-的安全性","Channels 的安全性",[12,822,823],{},"你可能會擔心說 Channels 會不會有安全問題，這邊簡單說明一下好了。",[12,825,826],{},"其實每一個被核准的 Channel Plugin 都會維護一個發送者白名單（Allowlist），只有你手動加入白名單的 ID 才能推送訊息，其他人的訊息會被直接丟棄，所以不用太擔心有人亂發訊息來搗亂。",[12,828,829],{},"Telegram 和 Discord 都是透過配對碼機制來建立白名單的：",[831,832,833,836,839,842],"ol",{},[71,834,835],{},"在 Telegram 或 Discord 上對你的 Bot 發送任何訊息",[71,837,838],{},"Bot 回覆一組配對碼",[71,840,841],{},"在 Claude Code 中輸入配對碼來核准",[71,843,844],{},"你的發送者 ID 就會被加入白名單",[12,846,847,848,850,851,854,855,857],{},"除此之外，你還可以透過 ",[75,849,229],{}," 參數來控制每次 Session 要啟用哪些 Channel。就算一個 MCP Server 被寫在 ",[75,852,853],{},".mcp.json"," 中，如果沒有被加入 ",[75,856,229],{},"，它也沒辦法推送訊息進來。",[12,859,860],{},"所以整體來看，安全機制是多層防護的：Plugin 白名單 + 配對碼驗證 + Session 級別的啟用控制，用起來是不用太擔心的。",[29,862,864],{"id":863},"channels-vs-remote-control-vs-龍蝦openclaw","Channels vs Remote Control vs 龍蝦（OpenClaw）",[12,866,867],{},"看到這邊，你可能會好奇說 Channels 跟之前介紹過的 Remote Control 還有龍蝦有什麼不同，這邊簡單整理一下：",[869,870,871,890],"table",{},[872,873,874],"thead",{},[875,876,877,881,884,887],"tr",{},[878,879,880],"th",{},"項目",[878,882,883],{},"Channels",[878,885,886],{},"Remote Control",[878,888,889],{},"龍蝦（OpenClaw）",[891,892,893,908,922,934,947],"tbody",{},[875,894,895,899,902,905],{},[896,897,898],"td",{},"核心概念",[896,900,901],{},"外部事件推送到 Claude Code",[896,903,904],{},"手機\u002F瀏覽器直接操控 Claude Code",[896,906,907],{},"透過聊天平台操控電腦",[875,909,910,913,916,919],{},[896,911,912],{},"支援平台",[896,914,915],{},"Telegram、Discord（可擴充）",[896,917,918],{},"claude.ai\u002Fcode、Claude App",[896,920,921],{},"多種聊天平台",[875,923,924,927,930,932],{},[896,925,926],{},"雙向溝通",[896,928,929],{},"支援",[896,931,929],{},[896,933,929],{},[875,935,936,939,942,944],{},[896,937,938],{},"官方支援",[896,940,941],{},"Anthropic 官方",[896,943,941],{},[896,945,946],{},"第三方",[875,948,949,952,955,958],{},[896,950,951],{},"適用情境",[896,953,954],{},"想透過聊天平台推送事件或訊息",[896,956,957],{},"想直接操控 Claude Code Session",[896,959,960],{},"想用聊天平台操控整台電腦",[12,962,963],{},"簡單來講：",[68,965,966,971,976],{},[71,967,968,970],{},[24,969,886],{}," 適合你想要「直接操控」Claude Code Session 的情境，就像拿著遙控器一樣。",[71,972,973,975],{},[24,974,883],{}," 更偏向「事件驅動」，像是把 CI 結果、監控警報、聊天訊息推送進來，讓 Claude 自動處理。",[71,977,978,980],{},[24,979,889],{}," 則是第三方的方案，功能更泛用，但相對來講沒有官方的穩定性保障。",[29,982,983],{"id":983},"延伸閱讀",[12,985,986],{},"關於 Claude Code 生態系，這幾篇我之前寫過的也滿值得一讀：",[68,988,989,997,1005],{},[71,990,991,996],{},[90,992,995],{"href":993,"rel":994},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fai\u002F20260128\u002F374686091\u002F",[94],"想用 Claude Code 開發？這篇帶你從入門到進階","：Claude Code 完整入門指南。",[71,998,999,1004],{},[90,1000,1003],{"href":1001,"rel":1002},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fai\u002F20260319\u002F738324368\u002F",[94],"Claude Cowork Dispatch 與 Remote Control - 用手機遠端控制你的 AI Agent","：Channels 之外另一個官方的遠端方案。",[71,1006,1007,1012],{},[90,1008,1011],{"href":1009,"rel":1010},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fgit\u002F20260121\u002F2025687513\u002F",[94],"Git Worktree 是什麼？一個專案同時跑多個 AI Agent 的秘訣","：搭配 Channels 並行任務的好搭檔。",[1014,1015,1016],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}",{"title":121,"searchDepth":1018,"depth":1018,"links":1019},2,[1020,1021,1022,1026,1027,1028,1029,1030,1031],{"id":31,"depth":1018,"text":31},{"id":43,"depth":1018,"text":44},{"id":62,"depth":1018,"text":63,"children":1023},[1024],{"id":107,"depth":1025,"text":108},3,{"id":183,"depth":1018,"text":184},{"id":301,"depth":1018,"text":302},{"id":536,"depth":1018,"text":537},{"id":819,"depth":1018,"text":820},{"id":863,"depth":1018,"text":864},{"id":983,"depth":1018,"text":983},"AI","2026-03-20 14:31:43","你有在用龍蝦（OpenClaw）來遠端操控電腦嗎？其實 Claude Code 也有類似的功能叫做「Channels」，它可以讓你透過 Telegram 或 Discord 把訊息推送到正在運行的 Claude Code Session 中，讓 Claude 幫你完成任務。這篇文章就來帶大家認識 Channels 的概念、設定方式以及實際使用情境。","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fai\u002Fopenclaw-claude-code-channels","7",{"title":6,"description":1034},false,"ai\u002F不想用龍蝦-OpenClaw-來試試看-Claude-Code-channels-吧！",[1032,1045,1046,1047,1048,1049],"Claude Code","Claude Code Channels","Telegram","Discord","AI Agent",null,"2026-05-12 09:00:00","\u002Fai\u002F20260320\u002F2827818448\u002F","DEXBQB_c8GDBR6PJbJFKJP_qcIrB9dub8AUDN8ymH3s",{"newer":1055,"older":1059},{"url":1056,"title":1057,"date":1058},"\u002Fai\u002F20260326\u002F73911729\u002F","2026 年 AI Coding 工具怎麼選？GitHub Copilot、Cursor、Claude Code、Kiro 與 Antigravity 完整比較","2026-03-26 12:00:00",{"url":1060,"title":1003,"date":1061},"\u002Fai\u002F20260319\u002F738324368\u002F","2026-03-19 10:00:00",[1063,1068,1072],{"url":1064,"title":1065,"date":1066,"readingMinutes":1067},"\u002Fai\u002F20260629\u002F2995176290\u002F","新版 Claude Code 終端機攔截滑鼠點擊超煩！用 CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_MOUSE_CLICKS 環境變數把它關掉","2026-06-29 18:00:00","2",{"url":1069,"title":1070,"date":1071,"readingMinutes":1040},"\u002Fai\u002F20260627\u002F1947382651\u002F","design.md？如果你使用 AI 畫面總是跑掉，那肯定是因為你沒導入 Google 的 design.md","2026-06-27 12:00:00",{"url":1073,"title":1074,"date":1075,"readingMinutes":1076},"\u002Fai\u002F20260622\u002F4283716095\u002F","讓 gh-pages 的 \u002Fllms.txt 回傳 text\u002Fmarkdown：Cloudflare 回應標頭轉換規則教學","2026-06-22 14:00:00","3",1784020329877]